        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1868-10-07T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1868-10-07T00:00:00-05:00" n="342" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d342">
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram per cable.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <head>
                    <persName type="from">Mr. La Reintrie</persName> to <persName type="to">Mr. Seward</persName>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Consulate General of the United
                                        States</hi>, <hi rend="italic">Havana</hi>,</placeName>
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1868-10-07">
                            <hi rend="italic">October</hi> 7, 1868.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Hon. <hi rend="smallcaps">William H. Seward</hi>, <hi rend="italic">Secretary of State, Washington, D. C.</hi>:</p>
                <p>The captain general has ordered Santa Anna to leave Cuba for plotting,
                            while here, against the peace of Mexico.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>H. R. DE LA REINTRIE, <hi rend="italic">Vice-Consul
                                    General.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
